introduction 1 john lamb is a citizen of the united states who says he is the owner of copyright in a cartoon of a scruffy looking pig with sunglasses and a bandaid patch known as the "wave hog work".
2 mr lamb alleges that from 1996 onwards in australia companies controlled by mr donald algie, a former employee of the hog's breath saloon, have infringed his copyright in the work in various ways.
